- Mobile and desktop layouts both remain usable.

[todo][high][RM-034] Add progression graph overlay in the UI
Show reachable vs blocked critical nodes, key-item unlock points, and the first
failure edge when a generated map is invalid.
Files: `tools/server/public/app.js`, `tools/progression_validator.js`
Acceptance:
- UI explains why a bad seed failed, not just that it failed.

[todo][high][RM-035] Add command-preview support for map options
Keep showing the exact CLI command that corresponds to the current UI state,
